    "description": "Rhenus Logistics India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Chennai location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Rhenus Logistics India:\nRhenus Logistics India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rhenus Logistics India!",
